OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FThe Government has ordered a review of
OL,7,Fphysician associates (PA) and
OL,8,Fanaesthesia associates (AA) in the NHS
OL,9,Ffollowing a "toxic debate" and fears
OL,10,Fover patient safety.
OL,12,FThe review, which will be published in
OL,13,Fspring 2025, will examine the tasks
OL,14,Fthat PAs and AAs are allowed to
OL,15,Fundertake and look into measures to
OL,16,Fensure patients know when they are
OL,17,Fbeing seen by a medical associate,
OL,18,Frather than a doctor.
