OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FAnnouncing the review, the Health
OL,7,FSecretary, Wes Streeting, said there
OL,8,Fwere "legitimate concerns over
OL,9,Ftransparency for patients".
OL,11,FBereaved families who've campaigned
OL,12,Ffor better regulation have welcomed
OL,13,Fthe news saying patients desperately
OL,14,Fneed "clarity" and "renewed trust" in
OL,15,Fthe NHS.
OL,17,F30-year-old Emily Chesterton died from
OL,18,Fa pulmonary embolism after she was
OL,19,Fmisdiagnosed by a physician associate.
OL,20,FShe thought she had been seen by a GP.
