OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FHer parents are now taking legal
OL,7,Faction against the General Medical
OL,8,FCouncil, accusing it of putting
OL,9,Fpatients at risk by failing to
OL,10,Fdistinguish properly between the role
OL,11,Fof doctors and medical associate
OL,12,Fprofessions.
OL,14,FHer mother Marion Chesterton told ITV
OL,15,FNews she 'welcomes' this review.
OL,17,F"We desperately need clarity as to the
OL,18,Fexact role of a PA and renewed trust
OL,19,Fin our NHS," she said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
