OL,6,F"There must be set limits as to what a
OL,7,FPA can and cannot do, for all our
OL,8,Fsakes. There must be a definite
OL,9,Fdescription of the meaning of
OL,10,Fsupervision.
OL,12,F"There must be no more Emilys. We miss
OL,13,Fher every minute of the day, our
OL,14,Fprecious daughter had such a wonderful
OL,15,Flife ahead. This must not be allowed
OL,16,Fto happen to anyone else."
