OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FThey can take medical histories and
OL,7,Fhelp to diagnose patients, but they
OL,8,Fcannot prescribe or order x-rays.
OL,10,FIn recent years concerns have been
OL,11,Fraised following the deaths of people
OL,12,Fwho were treated by PAs and mistakes
OL,13,Fwere made.
OL,15,FIn September the Academy of Medical
OL,16,FRoyal Colleges wrote to the Health
OL,17,FSecretary and NHS England calling for
OL,18,Fa rapid review of PAs and AAs amid
OL,19,F"mounting concern" from doctors.
