OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FThe academy called for an
OL,7,Finvestigation into whether using
OL,8,Fmedical associates was safe, cost-
OL,9,Feffective and efficient.
OL,11,FThe government has now announced a
OL,12,Freview will take place, led by
OL,13,FProfessor Gillian Leng, who is
OL,14,FPresident of the Royal Society of
OL,15,FMedicine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
