OL,3,CGovernment orders review into role of
OL,4,Cphysician associates in the NHS
OL,6,FThe review is due to report in the
OL,7,Fspring and will include
OL,8,Frecommendations on how the roles
OL,9,Fshould work in the future, as part of
OL,10,Fthe government's 10 Year Plan for the
OL,11,FNHS.
OL,13,FThe Health and Social Care Secretary,
OL,14,FWes Streeting, said: "Many physician
OL,15,Fassociates are providing great care
OL,16,Fand freeing up doctors to do the
OL,17,Fthings only doctors can do.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
