OL,6,FBMA council chair Professor Phil
OL,7,FBanfield said: "You do not fly a plane
OL,8,Funder safety review, you ground it. So
OL,9,Fwe need to know what immediate safety
OL,10,Fmeasures NHS England will put in
OL,11,Fplace, how quickly they will pause
OL,12,Ftheir PA expansion plans, and in the
OL,13,Fmeantime if they will adopt the BMA's
OL,14,Fown guidelines to start protecting
OL,15,Fpatients now.
