OL,6,F"The NHS has failed to make the
OL,7,Femployment of associates safe for
OL,8,Fpatients. By allowing a free-for-all
OL,9,Fon what PAs can and can't do,
OL,10,Fhospitals have become a postcode
OL,11,Flottery in which patients don't know
OL,12,Fif they are being seen by a
OL,13,Fprofessional with the right skills.
OL,15,F"Only a clear, nationally agreed scope
OL,16,Fof practice, telling employers what
OL,17,FPAs can and can't do, will clear up
OL,18,Fthis mess. This review must lead to
OL,19,Fone."
